     C                     MOVE PTOKU     UTOKU   40
     C                     MOVE PSTR      UKAIS
     C                     MOVE PEND      UOWAR
     C                     MOVE *DATE     UHIZK
     C                     MOVE PTIME     KOTIME
     C                     MOVE PTIME     UTIME
     C                     MOVE TI,1      HD
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    TMEIG  16
      *    b]ﾆﾞﾑc
     C                     MOVE STMM      STMM1
